How to Run:
  1. Compile Exercise_Tetris, Block, previewBlock, and TetrisModifier java files.
  2. Run Exervise_Tetris.
  
How to play:
  * Use left/right mouse click to move block
  * Rotate blocks with the mouse wheel
  * Pause game by moving mouse cursor within the play screen
  * Replace a block by left clicking on the falling block
  * All GUI are interactive with the mouse clicks
